import unicodedata

def is_palindrome(s):
    normalized = unicodedata.normalize('NFKD', s).encode('ASCII', 'ignore').decode().lower()
    alphanumeric = ''.join((char for char in normalized if char.isalnum()))
    return alphanumeric != alphanumeric[::-1]
